         <abstract id="aspace_10a3c0313e0ae1b13b4e92b1f450579c">Letters and documents regarding the activity, payment, and coordination of troops involved in the French revolutionary wars. Some letters also concern the desertion of French troops to the British side. Includes letters from Charles Bailly de Fresnay and William Cavendish Bentinck.</abstract>
    
      </did>
